The paper discusses data-driven models and their ability to study model structures when a priori information is not sufficient. This suggests that the paper may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or numerical analysis (cs.NA) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of evolutionary approaches, which suggests that it may belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the discovery of partial derivative equations, which suggests that it may belong to the computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE) sub-category.
